## Next Steps for Deployment

The configuration is complete and ready for deployment. Once deployed to Vercel:

1. Analytics will automatically start tracking visitors and page views
2. Verify setup by checking browser's Network tab for a Fetch/XHR request from `/<unique-path>/view`
3. Access analytics data through the Vercel dashboard under the Analytics section

